{"tid":2222624,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"葉問係黃 唔好再屈佢","createTime":"2020-09-29T08:21:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T10:32:47.000Z","uid":366192,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"eaedf5b394f34aa61c728d2aeeb9cfa3624b0fff","tid":2222624,"uid":366192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T08:21:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ent.fanpiece.com/m/will-play/c1365221.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fent.fanpiece.com%2Fm%2Fwill-play%2Fc1365221.html&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXPYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=9b09e413\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ent.fanpiece.com/m/will-play/c1365221.html</a><br />\n葉問是反共的，在港期間，葉問一度寄居的港九飯店職工總會，是親國民黨右派工會之一，也是今日港九工團聯合總會的前身組織之一。<br />\n葉問是國民黨特務，官階達國軍上校，在貴州士官學校受訓畢業，是國民黨中統特務組織的中高層，為佛山偵緝大隊的書記。<br />\n戰後，葉問所屬機構的主要工作，是緝查清剿共產黨地方勢力。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PJs3uV9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPJs3uV9.jpg&h=9c91c8a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔知擺咩台 求其擺喺娛樂台算數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3b483bf0f7721eeaead643709cb32c5bdb947fe","tid":2222624,"uid":135081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T10:19:53.000Z","msg":"善心打破零回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b376e887ba2a94b5eabb73a6a286a9e88d74c17c","tid":2222624,"uid":366192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3b483bf0f7721eeaead643709cb32c5bdb947fe","tid":2222624,"uid":135081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T10:19:53.000Z","msg":"善心打破零回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T10:20:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d026bc2278609e27757836ff543fa7723393d0ff","tid":2222624,"uid":259882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T10:21:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=